        <body>
      
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York 79 Duane St</placeName></p>
			<p rend="align(right)"><date>August 12&#44; 49</date></p>
			<p>To the <addressee>Revd I Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Dr Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">I beg to enclose Ten Dollars for the amnt.<lb/> of books I bought of you&#59; viz&#58; one <add>Hebrew</add> &#38; one <add>Hebrew</add>&#44; and<lb/> with many thanks for the indulgence of credit</p>
          <p rend="indent(8)">I remain Dr Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(9)">Respectfully yours</p>
          <p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">A Loewe</persName></p>
			<p>P. S. I should like very much to have the underneath inserted in your<lb/> valuable periodical&#44; but as I can not afford to spend much for it&#44;<lb/> you will oblige me by stating in a line or two the lowest you could<lb/> do it for me for the term of 1 month.</p>
			<p rend="align(center)"><hi rend="underline">Hebrew&#44; German&#44; and English taught</hi></p>
			<p><persName>Mr Adolph Loewe</persName> &#40;brother of <persName>Dr L. Loewe</persName> of <placeName>London</placeName>&#41; begs<lb/> to inform his friends &#38; public in general that&#44; he intends devoting a<lb/> few of his leisure hours to leading <hi rend="underline"><sic>privat</sic> classes</hi> in the Hebrew<lb/> German &#38; English languages either at my own residence <placeName>79 Duane St<lb/> New York</placeName>&#44; or at that of the pupils&#44;&#44;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><add>&#63;</add> Terms moderate</p>

          
        </body>
